{"tid":1093981,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[你們的郡主娘娘］陳鈺琪嚟緊仲有套<兩世歡>會上","createTime":"2019-04-06T03:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T09:33:30.000Z","uid":12558,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cdebb6fc126e75a9cd8cbfb137cfc3e5b515702c","tid":1093981,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T03:16:17.000Z","msg":"《兩世歡》是北京愛奇藝科技有限公司出品的輕懸疑古裝言情探案劇，由余翠華執導，於朦朧、陳鈺琪領銜主演。<br />\n<br />\n該劇根據「寂月皎皎」的同名小說改編，講述了貴公子與女捕快聯手破奇案，情節用一個個離奇的案件串聯起來，而隨著案件地展開，不僅關係到男女主之間情感的變化，還勾連著關係天下局勢的奪嫡之爭的故事。<br />\n鈺淇bb今次都會男扮女裝做捕快￼￼￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家等沈船￼￼￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BayHiUJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBayHiUJ.png&h=23933a28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/06/111528_a746550f0448c9c5ef204df46dcc801e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F06%2F111528_a746550f0448c9c5ef204df46dcc801e.png&h=fe8d2335&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/06/111530_194f6f170e5c85407017c1e0774073eb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F06%2F111530_194f6f170e5c85407017c1e0774073eb.png&h=f3b832c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/06/111533_9315f9efa8d4f0db4b4c592795272afa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F06%2F111533_9315f9efa8d4f0db4b4c592795272afa.png&h=06c9f6ce&s={SIZE}\" 